title: Cartier watch found in Hounslow charity shop raises £10,000

title: Meet Thom Browne, the stripe-obsessed designer who took on Adidas and won
description: Born in Allentown, Pennsylvania, Browne opened his first store in New York City in 2003 with five made-to-measure grey suits.
author: dsantana@businessinsider.com (Danni Santana)

title: A new partisan era of American education
description: Florida Gov. Ron DeSantis says he's protecting kids from indoctrination and political agendas, but the zeal with which he has pushed expansive efforts to remake the Florida education system also represents an effort to influence young minds.

title: Jill Biden to present Inauguration Day dresses at the Smithsonian
description: First lady Jill Biden will present both her Inauguration Day ensembles at the Smithsonian's National Museum of American History on Wednesday, the White House announced, as part of the museum's First Ladies Collection exhibition.
author: Donald Judd, Sonnet Swire

title: Obama responds to Tyre Nichols video: 'Vicious, unjustified beating'

title: The power couple at the center of Biden’s political universe
